Package org.opentcs.util

A collection of classes providing miscellaneous functions that are used throughout openTCS.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Comparators
    Some commonly used comparator implementations.
    CyclicTask
    A template for cyclic tasks.
    Enums
    Provides helper methods for working with enums.
    Environment
    Provides generic information about the openTCS environment.
    FileSystems
    This class provides helper methods for working with file systems.
    NumberParsers
    Provides methods for optimized parsing of numbers from character sequences.
    ObjectListCycler<E>
    Delivers objects from a given list infinitely, wrapping around at the end.
    QueueProcessor<E>
    A generic implementation of a queue processor.
    Streams
    This class provides helper methods for working with streams.
    UniqueStringGenerator<S>
    Provides a way to acquire unique strings.
    UniqueTimestampGenerator
    Instances of this class provide a way to acquire unique timestamps, working around the limitations of System.currentTimeMillis().
